            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="0"/>
                <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">καὶ ναίει νησοὺς ἐν θαλ</supplied>ίῃ μακά<supplied reason="lost">ρων <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ταμ<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> ου<supplied reason="lost">ραν</supplied>οῦ ἀστε <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Μηλε<supplied reason="lost">ίω</supplied>ν ὅς παράκοιτ<supplied reason="lost">ιν ἐλεῖ</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">οὐδείς</supplied> θνητὸς ἐὼν σὺν ἀθα<lb break="no" n="5"/>νάτοις βασιλεῦσιν οὐδεὶς τὴν <lb n="6"/>φ&amp;lt;ι=ΕΙ&amp;gt;λίαν θήκατο μέχρι τέλους. <lb n="7"/>οὗτος σῆμα τόδ' ἐσθλὸν ἑῇ κατέ<supplied reason="lost">θη</supplied><lb break="no" n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">κε συν</supplied>εύνῳ ἀντ' ἐρατῆς μ<supplied reason="lost">νήμης</supplied> <lb n="9"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>νοι ἁμ' ἁζόμεν<supplied reason="lost">ο</supplied>ς. γὰρ κου<supplied reason="lost">ριδί</supplied><lb break="no" n="10"/><supplied reason="lost">ην ἄλοχ</supplied>ον αυ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἐπ' <supplied reason="lost">ὀ</supplied>κτώ <lb n="11"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>της κούρην <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>χε<supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Metrik: elegische Disticha. Am Ende von Z. 4 ἐλεῖ statt ἐλεεῖ metrisch bedingt. Mehrere zusammengehörige Fragmente.</p>
